"height":1080,"file_path":"/Ab8mkHmkYADjU7wQiOkia9BzGvS.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":4.722},{"width":1808,"height":1017,"file_path":"/hZth9NCeXvvO7Xi98d8q34e1Ier.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":4.458},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/mSDsSDwaP3E7dEfUPWy4J0djt4O.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":4.3},{"width":1845,"height":1038,"file_path":"/mPEs6yhnimHhLqwDKKNpQ1Ju5HB.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3215,"height":1808,"file_path":"/rYC21h0FIt3Pb2BCX4sEbkGwO3w.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3839,"height":2160,"file_path":"/A0tq3gA5oiHF5IpdxavSyWgUtg3.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/rHi6MPPdCj775tIGOAZYJ8UZy1X.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","vote_average":3.334},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/s8qnMBMvqvz7FxtOxbztoA8IDif.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.066},{"width":1852,"height":1038,"file_path":"/b5xn9wkLWcJ5EGXLChtZVuoaJSU.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.066},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/xIyiEuvUawp7XKN4nshO1zdDGpm.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.066},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/eyaygChVcUyv2gOVAJl8OUwoYm2.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T10:38:09.574+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Spirited Away","runtime":125,"tagline":"Beyond the tunnel was a mysterious town.","homepage":"https://gkids.com/films/spirited-away","overview":"A young girl, Chihiro, becomes trapped in a strange new world of spirits. When her parents undergo a mysterious transformation, she must call upon the courage she never knew she had to free her family."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Chihiros Reise ins Zauberland","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Als die kleine Chihiro mit ihren Eltern während eines Ausflugs einen dunklen Tunnel durchquert, ahnt sie noch nicht, was sie auf der anderen Seite erwarten wird. Denn dort liegt eine für Menschen normalerweise unsichtbare Stadt der Geister. Zu allem Übel muss Chihiro dann auch noch feststellen, dass sich ihre Eltern in Schweine verwandelt haben und sie selbst plötzlich unsichtbar zu werden scheint..."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Chihiro Szellemországban","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chihiro, a tízéves, önfejű kislány meg van győződve arról, hogy az egész világ körülötte forog - épp ezért képtelen belenyugodni abba, hogy szüleivel új városba költözik, és csalódottságát meg sem próbálja leplezni az utazás alatt. Amikor az erdőben eltévedve egy különös zsákutca végére érnek, a kis család rábukkan egy sötét alagútra, amelynek másik végén szellemváros fogadja őket. Az üres utcákon fejedelmi lakomától roskadoznak az asztalok: az éhes szülők mohón a finom ételekre vetik magukat, ám hamarosan disznóvá változnak, amikor a városban felbukkannak a valódi vacsoravendégek. Az eldugott mesevilág lakói ősi istenek és más csodalények, uralkodója pedig Yubaba, a gonosz boszorkány. Chihiro csak akkor mentheti meg szüleit, ha hasznossá teszi magát Szellemországban és munkát talál magának a banya hatalmas fürdőházában."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"千与千寻","runtime":125,"tagline":"隧道的另一头，是不可思议的小镇","homepage":"https://www.ghibli.jp/works/chihiro/","overview":"小女孩千寻被困在一个陌生的精灵世界。当她的父母发生神秘变化后，她必须鼓起自己从未发现的勇气，才能解救自己，并将家人带回外面的世界。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Henkien kätkemä","runtime":126,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Oscar-palkitussa piirretyssä Chihiro- tyttönen eksyy vanhempiensa kanssa muuttomatkalla syrjäiselle metsätielle. Sieltä löytyy hylätty ravintola, jonka pöydät notkuvat ruokaa. Isä ja äiti ahmivat vatsansa täyteen, mutta Chihiro ei koske sapuskaan. Aamulla isä ja äiti ovat muuttuneet sioiksi, ja paikka paljastuu henkiolentojen lomakohteeksi. Fantastinen piirrostarina kiehtoo yhtä lailla lapsia ja aikuisia."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"El viaje de Chihiro","runtime":122,"tagline":"El túnel llevó a Chihiro a una ciudad misteriosa...","homepage":"http://www.labutaca.net/elviajedechihiro","overview":"Durante el traslado de su familia a los suburbios, una niña de 10 años de edad deambula por un mundo gobernado por dioses, brujas y espíritus, y donde los humanos se convierten en bestias."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Spirited Away","runtime":126,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://triart.se/filmer/spirited-away/","overview":"På väg till sitt nya hus kör den 10-årige Chihiro och hennes familj vilse. Plötsligt står de framför en tunnel som visar sig leda till en spökstad - en värld bebodd av urgamla gudar och magiska varelser som styrs av en demonisk härskarinna, Yubaba. Chihiro får en vän i den gåtfulla Haku, som hjälper henne att överleva i denna nya och konstiga värld."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Le Voyage de Chihiro","runtime":126,"tagline":"Un tunnel qui emmènera cette petite fille vers un monde mystérieux.","homepage":"http://movies.disney.com/spirited-away","overview":"Chihiro, 10 ans, a tout d’une petite fille capricieuse. Elle s’apprête à emménager avec ses parents dans une nouvelle demeure. Sur la route, la petite famille se retrouve face à un immense bâtiment rouge au centre duquel s’ouvre un long tunnel. De l’autre côté du passage se dresse une ville fantôme. Les parents découvrent dans un restaurant désert de nombreux mets succulents et ne tardent pas à se jeter dessus. Ils se retrouvent alors transformés en cochons. Prise de panique, Chihiro s’enfuit et se dématérialise progressivement. L’énigmatique Haku se charge de lui expliquer le fonctionnement de l’univers dans lequel elle vient de pénétrer. Pour sauver ses parents, la fillette va devoir faire face à la terrible sorcière Yubaba, qui arbore les traits d’une harpie méphistophélique."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"La città incantata","runtime":125,"tagline":"Il tunnel porta Chihiro in una città misteriosa...","homepage":"","overview":"La piccola Chihiro non sopporta l'idea di traslocare e di perdere i propri amici, ma non può far niente per impedirlo. Proprio quando la famiglia è in viaggio verso la nuova casa, il padre imbocca una strada sterrata che termina davanti a un tunnel misterioso. I genitori sceglieranno di attraversarlo nonostante le rimostranze di Chihiro, per giungere a un parco dei divertimenti abbandonato, almeno apparentemente."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Унесённые призраками","runtime":125,"tagline":"«Туннель привел Тихиро в таинственный город ...»","homepage":"","overview":"Тихиро с мамой и папой переезжает в новый дом. Заблудившись по дороге, они оказываются в странном пустынном городе, где их ждет великолепный пир. Родители с жадностью набрасываются на еду и к ужасу девочки превращаются в свиней, став пленниками злой колдуньи Юбабы. Теперь, оказавшись одна среди волшебных существ и загадочных видений, Тихиро должна придумать, как избавить своих родителей от чар коварной старухи."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"A Viagem de Chihiro","runtime":125,"tagline":"O túnel levou Chihiro para uma cidade misteriosa ...","homepage":"","overview":"Do mago da animação Hayao Miyazaki (\"A Princesa Mononoke\", \"O Meu Vizinho Totoro\", \"O Castelo Andante\" ou \"Ponyo à Beira-Mar”) este filme é direccionado a todas as idades e conta a história de Chihiro, uma menina de dez anos que descobre um mundo secreto. Quando os pais sofrem uma estranha transformação, Chihiro vê-se a entrar num lugar repleto de monstros e seres lendários, onde é obrigada a trabalhar para Yubaba, uma terrível bruxa com uma enorme cabeça e um corpo pequenino. Para salvar a família, Chihiro vive as mais fantásticas aventuras. Óscar de melhor filme de animação, o filme venceu, em ex-aequo com Domingo Sangrento de Paul Greengrass, o Urso de Ouro na edição de 2002 do Festival de Cinema de Berlim."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":125,"tagline":"トンネルのむこうは、不思議の町でした。","homepage":"https://www.ghibli.jp/works/chihiro/","overview":"両親と共に引越し先の新しい家へ向かう10歳の少女、千尋。しかし彼女はこれから始まる新しい生活に大きな不安を感じていた。やがて千尋たちの乗る車はいつの間にか“不思議の町”へと迷い込んでしまう。その奇妙な町の珍しさにつられ、どんどん足を踏み入れていく両親。が、彼らは“不思議の町”の掟を破ったために豚にされてしまう。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Chihiro og heksene","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chihiro og hendes forældre er på vej til deres nye hjem, men da hendes far forsøger med en genvej havner familien på en øde, mudret landevej. Som i et drømmesyn når de frem til en forladt forlystelsespark og en restaurant fyldt med mad, men uden gæster og personale. Mens forældrene kaster sig over maden, fornemmer Chihiro en fare og som mørket falder på oplever hun til sin skræk, at området er fyldt med ånder og hendes forældre forheksede. Snart får hun hjælp af den mystiske dreng Haku i et overdådigt eventyr fyldt med spænding, sjov og uhygge"},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Spirited Away: W krainie Bogów","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://gutekfilm.pl/spirited-away-w-krainie-bogow-hayao-miyazaki","overview":"Chihiro jest kapryśną, upartą dziesięcioletnią dziewczynką, która uważa, że cały świat powinien spełniać jej zachcianki. Gdy rodzice oznajmiają jej, że trzeba będzie wyprowadzić się z domu, Chihiro jest z tego powodu zła i nie myśli tego ukrywać. Zabrnąwszy w tajemniczą ślepą uliczkę, rodzina staje nagle przed ogromnym czerwonym domem, do którego wnętrza prowadzi niekończący się tunel, rozwarty jak ogromne usta. Wkrótce okazuje się, że Chihiro i jej rodzice wtargnęli do świata zamieszkanego przez starożytnych bogów i magiczne stworzenia, świata, którym rządzi demoniczna czarownica, okrutna Yubaba."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Cesta do fantazie","runtime":125,"tagline":"Na druhé straně tunelu se nacházelo tajemné město.","homepage":"","overview":"Desetiletá Chihiro je obyčejná japonská holčička. Když se se svými rodiči vydává poprvé do nového bydliště, jejich auto zabloudí na opuštěnou lesní cestu, vedoucí k záhadnému tunelu. Chihiro i její rodiče se vydají dovnitř a objeví cosi, co považují za opuštěný lunapark. Rodiče podlehnou lákavé nabídce občerstvení v opuštěných stáncích, ale záhy se promění ve vepře. Chihiro se snaží najít pomoc a narazí na tajuplného chlapce jménem Haku. Ten ji seznámí s duchy, kteří v noci lunapark obývají a najde jí zaměstnání u Yubaby, staré čarodějnice s malým tělem a velkou hlavou, která provozuje obrovské lázně, kam si chodí odpočinout milióny pozemských bohů a jiných fantastických bytostí. Zde se skrývá jediná možnost, jak může Chihiro zrušit zakletí svých rodičů a vrátit se do lidského světa."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Chihiro og heksene","runtime":126,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://starmedia.no/chihiro-og-heksene-3/","overview":"10 år gamle Chihiro skal flytte til en ny by sammen med foreldrene sine. På veien til det nye huset tar faren en snarvei – noe som får dramatiske konsekvenser. De kommer fram til noe som ser ut som en nedlagt fornøyelsespark, men det er faktisk et badehus for slitne ånder. Badehuset er kontrollert av den onde heksa Yubaba. Som straff for at foreldrene til Chihiro har tatt seg til rette på åndenes område og spist av maten deres, gjør Yubaba dem om til griser."},"name":"Bokmål","iso_639_1":"nb","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian Bokmål"},{"data":{"title":"Chihiro og heksene","runtime":126,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://starmedia.no/chihiro-og-heksene-3/","overview":"10 år gamle Chihiro skal flytte til en ny by sammen med foreldrene sine. På veien til det nye huset tar faren en snarvei – noe som får dramatiske konsekvenser. De kommer fram til noe som ser ut som en nedlagt fornøyelsespark, men det er faktisk et badehus for slitne ånder. Badehuset er kontrollert av den onde heksa Yubaba. Som straff for at foreldrene til Chihiro har tatt seg til rette på åndenes område og spist av maten deres, gjør Yubaba dem om til griser."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Spirited Away","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tijdens de verhuizing van haar familie naar een buitenwijk wandelt Chihiro, een 10-jarig meisje, een wereld binnen die geregeerd wordt door heksen en monsters, waar mensen veranderd worden in dieren. Chihiro moet in een groot badhuis werken om te overleven. Zal het haar lukken om terug te keren naar haar eigen wereld?"},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Ruhların Kaçışı","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Film, küçük Chihiro ve ailesinin yeni bir kasabaya taşınmalarıyla açılır. Yolculuk esnasında yolda gördükleri bir tünele dikkat eden aile, tünelin içerisinden geçtiklerinde karşılaştıkları fantastik dünyanın içerisinde büyülenirler. Ancak bu kasabada yolunda gitmeyen bir şeyler vardır, bu büyü kısa bir zaman sonra bozulacaktır. Ailesini kaybeden küçük Chihiro, babasını kurtarmak için korku dolu bir maceraya atılacaktır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Ταξίδι στη Χώρα των Θαυμάτων","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Η 10χρονη Τσιχίρο και οι γονείς της κατευθύνονται προς το νέο τους σπίτι στα προάστια, όταν ο πατέρας της αποφασίζει να κόψει δρόμο μέσα από ένα ερημικό δρομάκι. Η οικογένεια χάνεται σε ένα παράξενο τούνελ, που οδηγεί σε μια έρημη πόλη-φάντασμα και όπου, μυστηριωδώς, οι γονείς της Τσιχίρο θα μεταμορφωθούν σε γουρούνια. Η μικρή θα προσπαθήσει να λύσει τα μάγια, αντιμετωπίζοντας μάγισσες, πνεύματα και κάθε λογής θαύματα, με τη βοήθεια του Χάκου, ενός παράξενου παιδιού..."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"센과 치히로의 행방불명","runtime":124,"tagline":"금지된 세계의 문이 열렸다","homepage":"","overview":"평범한 열 살 짜리 소녀 치히로 식구는 이사 가던 중 길을 잘못 들어 낡은 터널을 지나가게 된다. 터널 저편엔 폐허가 된 놀이공원이 있었고 그곳엔 이상한 기운이 흘렀다. 인기척 하나 없는 이 마을의 낯선 분위기에 불길한 기운을 느낀 치히로는 부모님에게 돌아가자고 조르지만 부모님은 호기심에 들떠 마을 곳곳을 돌아다니기 시작한다. 어느 음식점에 도착한 치히로의 부모님은 그 곳에 차려진 음식들을 보고 즐거워하며 허겁지겁 먹어대다가 돼지로 변해버린다. 겁에 질려 당황하는 치히로에게 낯선 소년 하쿠가 나타나 빨리 이곳을 나가라고 소리치는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"המסע המופלא","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"כשהוריה מחליטים לעבור דירה, צ'יהירו נאלצת להיפרד מחבריה. היא מאד עצובה וכועסת על כך, והיא לא מסתירה את זה. בדרך לבית החדש מתפתה אביה להיכנס לפארק שעשועים מוזנח. בשעה שהוריה מוצאים לעצמם דוכן מזון, היא משוטטת ומקטרת, עד שמישהו מזהיר אותה להסתלק מהמקום לפני רדת החשיכה. אך כשהיא שבה להזהיר את הוריה היא מגלה כי הם כבר הפכו לחזירים. מכאן היא עתידה להיתקל בעוד ועוד יצורים משונים, ותצטרך לגלות אחריות כדי לשמור על זהותה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Gariem līdzi","runtime":0,"tagline":"Ceļš ieveda Čihiro noslēpumainajā pilsētā...","homepage":"","overview":"Gariem Līdzi ir japāņu animācijas filma, apbalvota ar Oskara balvu, par desmit gadus vecu meiteni, kas aizklīst no vecākiem un nokļūst pasaulē, ko pārvalda briesmoņveidīgi dzīvnieki. Viņas vecāki tiek pārvērsti par cūkām, līdzās citiem radījumiem. Vai viņa spēs atgriezties savā pasaulē?"},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"El viatge de Chihiro","runtime":0,"tagline":"Et farà somiar","homepage":"","overview":"Chihiro s'endinsa i ens porta amb ella a un món inquietant i incomprensible. Seguint-la de prop descobrirem aquells personatges que el fan segur i estimable, i sentirem que res pot vèncer la força del seu cor. Sense proposar-nos-ho, amb una emoció profunda, l'acompanyarem al tren que només fa el viatge d'anada, fins a terres inexplorades que seran ja per sempre casa nostra. Sublim."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"Віднесені привидами","runtime":124,"tagline":"По той бік тунелю було таємниче місто.","homepage":"","overview":"Маленька Чіхіро разом з мамою і татом переїздять в новий будинок. Заблукавши по дорозі, вони опиняються в дивному пустинному місті, де їх чекає чудовий бенкет. Батьки з жадібністю накидаються на їжу і до жаху дівчинки перетворюються на свиней, ставши полоненими злої чаклунки Юбаби, володарки таємничого світу стародавніх богів і могутніх духів.  Тепер, опинившись одна серед магічних істот і загадкових бачень, відважна Чіхіро повинна придумати, як позбавити своїх батьків від чар підступної старої і врятуватися з страшного царства примар."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Отнесени от духове","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Изгубила се сред изоставен лунапарк, малката Чихиро скоро намира родителите си, превърнати в прасета, а самата себе си - на ръба на невидимостта. С падането на нощта изплува цял нов свят - огромен дом на прилепи, ръкодовен от магьосницата Юбаба и обитаван от милиони призраци, богове и гоблини. За хората място няма, но работата там е единствената надежда на Чихиро да спаси родителите си и себе си."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"神隱少女","runtime":125,"tagline":"曾發生過的事情不會忘記，只是想不起而已……","homepage":"","overview":"隧道的另一端，是一個不可思議的地方！ 一個不可能有的地點，一個不可能的事情竟然發生。 10歲的少女千尋和父母，被捲入人類不能踏入的世界。 在這個處處令人驚訝的地方，千尋感受到強大的無力感…和渺小的希望。 讓我在這裡工作吧！ 為解救被變成動物的父母，千尋求生的力量原本是沉睡的，現在終於被喚醒！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"A Viagem de Chihiro","runtime":126,"tagline":"Do outro lado do túnel havia uma cidade misteriosa.","homepage":"https://www.ghibli.jp/works/chihiro/","overview":"Chihiro e seus pais estão se mudando para uma cidade diferente. A caminho da nova casa, o pai decide pegar um atalho. Eles se deparam com uma mesa repleta de comida, embora ninguém esteja por perto. Chihiro sente o perigo, mas seus pais começam a comer. Quando anoitece, eles se transformam em porcos. Agora, apenas Chihiro pode salvá-los."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"El viaje de Chihiro","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Durante la mudanza de su familia a los suburbios, una huraña niña de 10 años de edad deambula por un mundo gobernado por dioses, brujas y espíritus, y donde los humanos se convierten en bestias."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"มิติวิญญาณมหัศจรรย์","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เรื่องราวของ “จิฮิโระ” เด็กหญิงวัย 10 ปี จอมงอแงและดื้อรัน ที่่กำลังอยู่ระหว่างการเดินทางย้ายมาบ้านใหม่กับพ่อแม่ แต่กลับหลงเข้าไปในอีกมิติหนึ่งโดยบังเอิญ ทำให้พ่อแม่ของเธอถูกสาปเป็นหมู และเธอจะต้องติดอยู่ในมิติที่เต็มไปด้วยภูตผีและเรื่องราวมหัศจรรย์ที่เธอไม่เคยเห็นที่ไหนมาก่อน"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Зачарани град","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Радња прати Чихиро, десетогодишњу девојчицу која се са родитељима сели у градић у унутрашњости. Због грешке приликом скретања њихов ауто завршава на једносмерном путу који се завршава улазом у тунел. Одлучују да мало истраже околину и откривају напуштено место са забавним парком. Чихиро наилази на дечака који јој саопштава да је у опасности и приликом повратка код родитеља схвата да су исти претворени у свиње, а да је место пуно демона и духова, док су људи претворени у животиње…"},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Cesta do fantázie","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Cesta do fantázie je dobrodružná snímka, kde sa neodohrávajú boje, hlavná postava nemá nadprirodzené schopnosti ani sa tu neháda dobro so zlom. Rozprávanie o desaťročnom dievčatku, ktoré sa ocitne v čarovnom meste duchov, bôžikov a strašidiel, sa obíde bez schém a prvoplánových atrakcií sezónnych animovaných hitov. Naopak, divákov každého veku pohltí unikátnou víziou autora, vďaka ktorej každý záber dýcha čarovnosťou, hravosťou, nápaditosťou, ale aj melanchóliou a emotívnosťou"},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"La vojaĝo de Ĉihiro","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Amanta koro scipovas fari miraklojn. La knabino Ĉihiro kune kun siaj gepatroj aŭtomobile devojiĝas en arbaro kaj alvenas al mistera tunelo, kiun ili piede transiras kaj tuje troviĝas en magia lando. El la malmodereco de la gepatroj sekvas ke ili baldaŭ transformiĝas en porkojn. Nur Ĉihiro povas savi ilin, kaj por tio ŝi devas esti kuraĝa kaj labori en la magia banejo, kie dioj, fantomoj kaj monstroj banas sin."},"name":"Esperanto","iso_639_1":"eo","iso_3166_1":"EO","english_name":"Esperanto"},{"data":{"title":"Spirited Away","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Seorang anak perempuan berusia 10 tahun semakin jauh dari orangtuanya, memasuki dunia yang dikuasai oleh para binatang aneh yang mirip monster. Akankah dia bisa melihat kembali dunia seperti semula?"},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"شهر اشباح","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"دختری ۱۰ ساله در نقل مکان خانواده‌اش به حومه شهر، در دنیایی سرگردان می‌شود که توسط خدایان، جادوگرها، و هیولاها اداره می‌شود؛ جایی که انسان‌ها به شکل حیوانات در می‌آیند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Avanture Male Chihiro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Na putu prema njihovoj novoj kući na selu, mlada Chihiro i njeni roditelji nailaze na tunel koji vodi u čudan napušteni grad. Roditelji otkrivaju restoran pun primamljive hrane i odmah se bace na jelo dok djevojčica nastavlja istraživati. No kad padne noć grad postaje pun duhova i goblina. Chihiro nalazi svoje roditelje pretvorene u svinje, a put nazad je nemoguć. Ona mora pronaći način kako da roditelje ponovno pretvori u ljude i izbavi se iz začaranog grada."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"千與千尋","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"某一天，年僅 10 歲的荻野千尋跟著父母坐在車上，準備一同前往要搬入的新家。在路途當中，千尋的父親因開錯方向，來到一條有著隧道入口的小徑。千尋的父母在一時好奇心下，帶著她前往隧道裏頭一探究竟。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Călătoria lui Chihiro","runtime":124,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chihiro rătăcește într-o lume magică unde domnește o vrăjitoare care îi transformă în animale pe cei care nu i se supun."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Stebuklingi Šihiros nuotykiai Dvasių pasaulyje","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Maža mergaitė Šihira kartu su savo tėvais paslaptingu miško tuneliu patenka į keistą dar neregėtą miestą: visos gatvės išstatytos stalais, ant stalų gardžiausi patiekalai ir gėrimai. Šihiros tėvai pasiduoda pagundai ir ima ragauti visų gėrybių. Deja, netrukus užburtame Dvasių pasaulyje jie virsta kiaulėmis. Šihira suvokia likusi viena paslaptingame mieste, kurioje nematomi gyventojai nemato ir jos pačios. Mergaitė stoja į kovą prieš Dvasias, Paslaptis, Burtus ir Užkeikimus, kad susigrąžintų savo tėvus."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"المخطوفة","runtime":0,"tagline":"إختطاف سان وتشيهيرو بعيداً","homepage":"","overview":"تتجول \"شيهيرو\" في عالم سحري تحكمه ساحرة - تقوم بتحويل كل من يعصيها إلى حيوانات."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Vùng Đất Linh Hồn","runtime":135,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Câu chuyện kể về cô bé bướng bỉnh Chihiro. Gia đình của Chihiro chuyển từ thành phố về quê sinh sống, và Chihiro chẳng thích thú tí nào với sự thay đổi này.  Bố của Chihiro là một tay lái xe tệ hại và có một trí nhớ \"quá tồi\", ông đã lái xe lạc đường đến một thành phố bị bỏ hoang, không bóng người. Bị cuốn hút bởi mùi vị thơm ngon của thức ăn, bố mẹ của Chihiro bắt đầu \"thưởng thức\", nhưng kết quả họ bị biến thành những con heo mập. Còn thành phố không người kia, sau khi trời tối, tất cả sống dậy, những bóng ma bắt đầu xuất hiện và hoạt động. Cô bé bướng bỉnh phải làm gì để cứu bố mẹ mình và thoát khỏi đây?"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Čudežno potovanje","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Desetletna deklica Čihiro je prepričana, da se mora svet podrediti vsaki njeni muhi. Ko ji starši povedo, da se morajo preseliti, je besna in sploh ne poskuša skriti jeze. Med selitvijo v novo hišo prispejo do konca skrivnostne slepe ulice, pred ogromno rdečo stavbo, pod katero zeva neskončen predor, podoben orjaškim ustom. Znajdejo se v svetu pradavnih bogov in čarobnih bitij, ki mu vlada demonska čarovnica Jubaba. Deklica se poda na pot, da bi starše rešila iz začaranega sveta."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"स्पिरिटेड अवे","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"एक युवा लड़की, चीहिरो, आत्माओं की एक अजीब नई दुनिया में फंस जाती है। जब उसके माता-पिता एक रहस्यमय परिवर्तन से गुजरते हैं, तो उसे उस साहस को बुलाना चाहिए जिसे वह कभी नहीं जानती थी कि उसे अपने परिवार को मुक्त करना है।"},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Chihiroren Bidaia","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chihiro 10 urteko neska da, eta bere gurasoek -Akio eta Yugo- etxez aldatu behar dutela esaten diotenean, asko nahigabetzen da. Etxe berrirako bidean galdu egiten dira eta tunel misteriotsu bat aurkitzen dute, eta jakinguraz beterik, barnera doaz. Familia txikia itxuraz abandonaturiko herri baten kalean sartzen da, jatetxez betea, eta aitak bazkaltzeko leku on bat topatzen du. Baina gurasoak jan eta berehala sorginkeria baten ondorioz txerri bihurtzen dira. Chihiro mundu misteriotsu eta magiko horretan dagoen bainuetxean bizirauten saiatu beharko da."},"name":"euskera","iso_639_1":"eu","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Basque"},{"data":{"title":"Скрадзеныя прывідамі","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Маленькая дзяўчынка Ціхора разам са сваёй сям'ёй перабіраецца ў новы дом. На шляху да яго сям'я трапляе ў незвычайны горад, дзе іх сустракаюць раскошным балем. Бацькі дзяўчынкі, варта было ім толькі пакаштаваць пачастункі, ператвараюцца ў свінняў. І зараз Ціхора трэба будзе знайсці спосаб, каб вызваліць сваіх родных з пасткі злой вядзьмаркі."},"name":"беларуская мова","iso_639_1":"be","iso_3166_1":"BY","english_name":"Belarusian"},{"data":{"title":"Vaimudest viidud","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kümneaastane Chihiro satub oma perega võlutud metsa, kus ta vanemad muutuvad sigadeks. Üksinda fantaasiamaailmas vanemaid otsival tüdrukul tuleb ohverdada oma nimi - tema identiteedi võti. Chihiro, uue nimega Sen, satub tööle nõid Yubaba saunamajas ja kohtub seal eriskummaliste tegelastega - väsinud vaimude ning hingedega, kes otsivad puhkust inimeste maailmast."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"მოჩვენებებით გატაცებულნი","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ოჯახი ყიდულობს სახლს შორეულ და ძალიან მშვიდ სოფელში. მათ ყავთ ათი წლის ქალიშვილი ჩიხირა, რომელიც, როგორც ყველა მისი ასაკის ბავშვი ძალიან ცნობისმოყვარეა. ერთერთ მზიან დღეს ის პოულობს, რაღაცას გვირაბის მაგვარს, რომლლის მეორე მხარეს სხვა სამყაროა, რომელიც განსხვავდება ამ სამყაროსგან თავისი უცნაურობებით, საიდუმლოებით და იდუმალებით. უცნობი ძალა პატარა გოგონას შეიტყუებს გვირაბში და ის აღმოჩნდება სხვა, იმ სამყაროში, რომელსაც შორიდან ხედავდა. თავიდან მას ეშინოდა, მაგრამ მერე მიეჩვია და ნახა ძალები აჯობოს თავის თავში შიშის გრძნობას და სამუშაოზე მოწყობაც მოახერხა."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Le voyage de Chihiro","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Une fillette qui s'est aventurée dans une étrange station thermale où viennent se purifier les dieux se retrouve sous le joug d'une sorcière."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Spirited Away","runtime":125,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Si Chihiro, isang 10 taong gulang na batang babae, ay patungo sa bago nilang bahay, kasama ang kanyang mga magulang. Gayunpaman, nakakaramdam siya ng matinding pagkabalisa tungkol sa bagong buhay na sisimulan niya. Hindi nagtagal, ang kotse na kanilang sinasakyan ay natitisod sa isang \"misteryosong bayan.\" Dahil sa pagiging kakaiba ng bayan, ang kanyang mga magulang ay patuloy na nakikipagsapalaran dito. Gayunpaman, sila ay naging mga baboy para sa paglabag sa mga patakaran ng \"mahiwagang bayan.\""},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"5d17c91385702e001eb921db","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5d17c91385702e001eb921db","author":"ZeBlah","content":"One of the great \"masters\" of the anime art. Somehow, if I would personally associate \"Akira\" to \"self-destruction\", then this anime would be the opposite :)","created_at":"2019-06-29T20:24:51.877Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:58:23.763Z","author_details":{"name":"ZeBlah","rating":10,"username":"TheBlah","avatar_path":"/d7rZv7xFhXHy0OLbVc2byJiZwEU.jpg"}},{"id":"67702ac55f1c4fa473612f7a","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/67702ac55f1c4fa473612f7a","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2024-12-28T16:43:49.694Z","updated_at":"2024-12-28T16:43:49.830Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":7,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":4935,"adult":false,"title":"Howl's Moving Castle","video":false,"overview":"Sophie, a young milliner, is turned into an elderly woman by a witch who enters her shop and curses her. She encounters a wizard named Howl and gets caught up in his resistance to fighting for the king.","genre_ids":[14,16,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.9617,"vote_count":10832,"poster_path":"/13kOl2v0nD2OLbVSHnHk8GUFEhO.jpg","release_date":"2004-09-09","vote_average":8.387,"backdrop_path":"/pjy0T63vIFYvxRSJ3ZtjB4tmWV4.jpg","original_title":"ハウルの動く城","original_language":"ja"},{"id":128,"adult":false,"title":"Princess Mononoke","video":false,"overview":"Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a demonized boar god and must journey to the west to find a cure. Along the way, he encounters San, a young human woman fighting to protect the forest, and Lady Eboshi, who is trying to destroy it. Ashitaka must find a way to bring balance to this conflict.","genre_ids":[12,14,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.3567,"vote_count":8776,"poster_path":"/cMYCDADoLKLbB83g4WnJegaZimC.jpg","release_date":"1997-07-12","vote_average":8.323,"backdrop_path":"/gl0jzn4BupSbL2qMVeqrjKkF9Js.jpg","original_title":"もののけ姫","original_language":"ja"},{"id":8392,"adult":false,"title":"My Neighbor Totoro","video":false,"overview":"Two sisters move to the country with their father in order to be closer to their hospitalized mother, and discover the surrounding trees are inhabited by Totoros, magical spirits of the forest. When the youngest runs away from home, the older sister seeks help from the spirits to find her.","genre_ids":[14,16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.3967,"vote_count":8627,"poster_path":"/rtGDOeG9LzoerkDGZF9dnVeLppL.jpg","release_date":"1988-04-16","vote_average":8.063,"backdrop_path":"/6O1mOoTXuc1WqjKd2R7MFQHZ7Eb.jpg","original_title":"となりのトトロ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":372058,"adult":false,"title":"Your Name.","video":false,"overview":"High schoolers Mitsuha and Taki are complete strangers living separate lives. But one night, they suddenly switch places. Mitsuha wakes up in Taki’s body, and he in hers. This bizarre occurrence continues to happen randomly, and the two must adjust their lives around each other.","genre_ids":[16,10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.3461,"vote_count":12297,"poster_path":"/q719jXXEzOoYaps6babgKnONONX.jpg","release_date":"2016-08-26","vote_average":8.478,"backdrop_path":"/8x9iKH8kWA0zdkgNdpAew7OstYe.jpg","original_title":"君の名は。","original_language":"ja"},{"id":496243,"adult":false,"title":"Parasite","video":false,"overview":"All unemployed, Ki-taek's family takes peculiar interest in the wealthy and glamorous Parks for their livelihood until they get entangled in an unexpected incident.","genre_ids":[35,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":32.1216,"vote_count":20162,"poster_path":"/7IiTTgloJzvGI1TAYymCfbfl3vT.jpg","release_date":"2019-05-30","vote_average":8.494,"backdrop_path":"/hiKmpZMGZsrkA3cdce8a7Dpos1j.jpg","original_title":"기생충","original_language":"ko"},{"id":637,"adult":false,"title":"Life Is Beautiful","video":false,"overview":"A touching story of an Italian book seller of Jewish ancestry who lives in his own little fairy tale. His creative and happy life would come to an abrupt halt when his entire family is deported to a concentration camp during World War II. While locked up he tries to convince his son that the whole thing is just a game.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.5302,"vote_count":13800,"poster_path":"/mfnkSeeVOBVheuyn2lo4tfmOPQb.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-20","vote_average":8.44,"backdrop_path":"/6aNKD81RHR1DqUUa8kOZ1TBY1Lp.jpg","original_title":"La vita è bella","original_language":"it"},{"id":12429,"adult":false,"title":"Ponyo","video":false,"overview":"When Sosuke, a young boy who lives on a clifftop overlooking the sea, rescues a stranded goldfish named Ponyo, he discovers more than he bargained for. Ponyo is a curious, energetic young creature who yearns to be human, but even as she causes chaos around the house, her father, a powerful sorcerer, schemes to return Ponyo to the sea.","genre_ids":[16,14,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.242,"vote_count":4708,"poster_path":"/yp8vEZflGynlEylxEesbYasc06i.jpg","release_date":"2008-07-19","vote_average":7.757,"backdrop_path":"/shqLeIkqPAAXM8iT6wVDiXUYz1p.jpg","original_title":"崖の上のポニョ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":497,"adult":false,"title":"The Green Mile","video":false,"overview":"A supernatural tale set on death row in a Southern prison, where gentle giant John Coffey possesses the mysterious power to heal people's ailments. When the cell block's head guard, Paul Edgecomb, recognizes Coffey's miraculous gift, he tries desperately to help stave off the condemned man's execution.","genre_ids":[14,18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.2168,"vote_count":18869,"poster_path":"/8VG8fDNiy50H4FedGwdSVUPoaJe.jpg","release_date":"1999-12-10","vote_average":8.504,"backdrop_path":"/b6HWTOxn1xevvyHU2K9ICvaRU6g.jpg","original_title":"The Green Mile","original_language":"en"},{"id":15370,"adult":false,"title":"The Cat Returns","video":false,"overview":"Young Haru rescues a cat from being run over, but soon learns it's no ordinary feline; it happens to be the Prince of the Cats.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,18,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.7361,"vote_count":2400,"poster_path":"/pqyY7IEWkCWNZ7EuRStQaJITEta.jpg","release_date":"2002-07-19","vote_average":7.132,"backdrop_path":"/tlQtvjwwTAAbNbtZ7IIGPlY50Hx.jpg","original_title":"猫の恩返し","original_language":"ja"},{"id":149870,"adult":false,"title":"The Wind Rises","video":false,"overview":"A lifelong love of flight inspires Japanese aviation engineer Jiro Horikoshi, whose storied career includes the creation of the A-6M World War II fighter plane.","genre_ids":[18,16,10749,10752,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.816,"vote_count":3288,"poster_path":"/jfwSexzlIzaOgxP9A8bTA6t8YYb.jpg","release_date":"2013-07-20","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/938lqhAQaO3hmLg44VbUR7OqlMs.jpg","original_title":"風立ちぬ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":10515,"adult":false,"title":"Castle in the Sky","video":false,"overview":"A young boy and a girl with a magic crystal must race against pirates and foreign agents in a search for a legendary floating castle.","genre_ids":[12,14,16,28,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.5401,"vote_count":4582,"poster_path":"/41XxSsJc5OrulP0m7TrrUeO2hoz.jpg","release_date":"1986-08-02","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/j2ZvLJyz163MlmBFsoaDYOwxgws.jpg","original_title":"天空の城ラピュタ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12477,"adult":false,"title":"Grave of the Fireflies","video":false,"overview":"In the final months of World War II, 14-year-old Seita and his sister Setsuko are orphaned when their mother is killed during an air raid in Kobe, Japan. After a falling out with their aunt, they move into an abandoned bomb shelter. With no surviving relatives and their emergency rations depleted, Seita and Setsuko struggle to survive.","genre_ids":[16,18,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0087,"vote_count":6364,"poster_path":"/k9tv1rXZbOhH7eiCk378x61kNQ1.jpg","release_date":"1988-04-16","vote_average":8.443,"backdrop_path":"/aHaqZpOL7UyVu0nKqp3SMz0o2E1.jpg","original_title":"火垂るの墓","original_language":"ja"},{"id":389,"adult":false,"title":"12 Angry Men","video":false,"overview":"The defense and the prosecution have rested and the jury is filing into the jury room to decide if a young Spanish-American is guilty or innocent of murdering his father. What begins as an open and shut case soon becomes a mini-drama of each of the jurors' prejudices and preconceptions about the trial, the accused, and each other.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.8187,"vote_count":9752,"poster_path":"/ow3wq89wM8qd5X7hWKxiRfsFf9C.jpg","release_date":"1957-04-10","vote_average":8.556,"backdrop_path":"/w4bTBXcqXc2TUyS5Fc4h67uWbPn.jpg","original_title":"12 Angry Men","original_language":"en"},{"id":155,"adult":false,"title":"The Dark Knight","video":false,"overview":"Batman raises the stakes in his war on crime. With the help of Lt. Jim Gordon and District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman sets out to dismantle the remaining criminal organizations that plague the streets. The partnership proves to be effective, but they soon find themselves prey to a reign of chaos unleashed by a rising criminal mastermind known to the terrified citizens of Gotham as the Joker.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":29.0324,"vote_count":35203,"poster_path":"/qJ2tW6WMUDux911r6m7haRef0WH.jpg","release_date":"2008-07-16","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/dqK9Hag1054tghRQSqLSfrkvQnA.jpg","original_title":"The Dark Knight","original_language":"en"},{"id":598,"adult":false,"title":"City of God","video":false,"overview":"In the poverty-stricken favelas of Rio de Janeiro in the 1970s, two young men choose different paths. Rocket is a budding photographer who documents the increasing drug-related violence of his neighborhood, while José “Zé” Pequeno is an ambitious drug dealer diving into a dangerous life of crime.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.983,"vote_count":8014,"poster_path":"/k7eYdWvhYQyRQoU2TB2A2Xu2TfD.jpg","release_date":"2002-08-30","vote_average":8.427,"backdrop_path":"/uvitbjFU4JqvMwIkMWHp69bmUzG.jpg","original_title":"Cidade de Deus","original_language":"pt"},{"id":680,"adult":false,"title":"Pulp Fiction","video":false,"overview":"A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gangster's moll and a washed-up boxer converge in this sprawling, comedic crime caper. Their adventures unfurl in three stories that ingeniously trip back and forth in time.","genre_ids":[53,80,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":23.9216,"vote_count":29708,"poster_path":"/vQWk5YBFWF4bZaofAbv0tShwBvQ.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-10","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/96hiUXEuYsu4tcnvlaY8tEMFM0m.jpg","original_title":"Pulp Fiction","original_language":"en"},{"id":11621,"adult":false,"title":"Porco Rosso","video":false,"overview":"In Italy in the 1930s, sky pirates in biplanes terrorize wealthy cruise ships as they sail the Adriatic Sea. The only pilot brave enough to stop the scourge is the mysterious Porco Rosso, a former World War I flying ace who was somehow turned into a pig during the war. As he prepares to battle the pirate crew's American ace, Porco Rosso enlists the help of spunky girl mechanic Fio Piccolo and his longtime friend Madame Gina.","genre_ids":[10751,35,16,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.3099,"vote_count":3626,"poster_path":"/8mIvSvnVBApfORL9N6S38Q7wD6A.jpg","release_date":"1992-07-18","vote_average":7.794,"backdrop_path":"/hnpNzxZRC9UHbk73c16XC1qEdEc.jpg","original_title":"紅の豚","original_language":"ja"},{"id":16859,"adult":false,"title":"Kiki's Delivery Service","video":false,"overview":"A young witch, on her mandatory year of independent life, finds fitting into a new community difficult while she supports herself by running an air courier service.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6261,"vote_count":4459,"poster_path":"/Aufa4YdZIv4AXpR9rznwVA5SEfd.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-29","vote_average":7.83,"backdrop_path":"/h5pAEVma835u8xoE60kmLVopLct.jpg","original_title":"魔女の宅急便","original_language":"ja"},{"id":51739,"adult":false,"title":"The Secret World of Arrietty","video":false,"overview":"14-year-old Arrietty and the rest of the Clock family live in peaceful anonymity as they make their own home from items \"borrowed\" from the house's human inhabitants. However, life changes for the Clocks when a human boy discovers Arrietty.","genre_ids":[14,16,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.8612,"vote_count":3088,"poster_path":"/3lSRaSjDp2nkXMQkzzjpRi3035O.jpg","release_date":"2010-07-16","vote_average":7.666,"backdrop_path":"/7Z7WVzJsSReG8B0CaPk0bvWD7tK.jpg","original_title":"借りぐらしのアリエッティ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":13,"adult":false,"title":"Forrest Gump","video":false,"overview":"A man with a low IQ has accomplished great things in his life and been present during significant historic events—in each case, far exceeding what anyone imagined he could do. But despite all he has achieved, his one true love eludes him.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.8264,"vote_count":29261,"poster_path":"/saHP97rTPS5eLmrLQEcANmKrsFl.jpg","release_date":"1994-06-23","vote_average":8.462,"backdrop_path":"/67HggiWaP9ZLv5sPYmyRV37yAJM.jpg","original_title":"Forrest Gump","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":589972,"adult":false,"title":"Little Vampire","video":false,"overview":"Little Vampire lives in a haunted house with a merry group of monsters, but he is bored stiff! One night, he secretly sneaks out of the manor along with his trusted bulldog, Phantomato, on a quest to find some new friends.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"popularity":0.3631,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/mLd9FVJTwnPO3ERv82ea5IZo6Hl.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-21","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/dAWrub4aTNMsh0pnYBiGPKZiREr.jpg","original_title":"Petit Vampire","original_language":"fr"},{"id":589973,"adult":false,"title":"SamSam","video":false,"overview":"SamSam, the smallest of the great heroes, has still not discovered his first superpower, while at home and at school, everyone has one! Faced with the worry of his parents and the mockery of his comrades, he goes in search of this hidden power. With the help of Mega, the new mysterious student of his school, Samsam embarks on this adventure full of cosmic monsters ...","genre_ids":[16,10751,878,12,35],"popularity":0.3545,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/nNMAglUfOuDuyAKYSmXzFkBeNha.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-05","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/5T2kiBvi169qnCY8ul3btCRfJuf.jpg","original_title":"SamSam","original_language":"fr"},{"id":418956,"adult":false,"title":"The Ugly Duckling","video":false,"overview":"An outcast duckling's search for a family to accept him leads to constant rejection before learning his true identity as a swan.","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.9617,"vote_count":183,"poster_path":"/nCkMoq2penMxvdhQa0LGwK1G6fJ.jpg","release_date":"1939-04-07","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/woMB1t6cBbS9xPzZzsv8DI7IOxV.jpg","original_title":"The Ugly Duckling","original_language":"en"},{"id":763577,"adult":false,"title":"Spiritpact","video":false,"overview":"Yang Jinghua, a young heir to a family of exorcists, is left struggling alone after his parents’ deaths. Barely surviving, he encounters the wealthy and skilled exorcist Duanmu Xi while trying to fend off a spirit. After a fatal accident, Yang awakens to find himself in a contract with Duanmu Xi, marking the start of his new life.","genre_ids":[14],"popularity":0.2472,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/gQfa44P8piUHJ8A7bP6j0PXBNEy.jpg","release_date":"2018-03-11","vote_average":2.7,"backdrop_path":"/6P5Y2u2HrnOrTVQXTNDUNsJpSiS.jpg","original_title":"灵契","original_language":"zh"},{"id":647,"adult":false,"title":"Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children","video":false,"overview":"Two years have passed since the final battle with Sephiroth. Though Midgar, city of mako, city of prosperity, has been reduced to ruins, its people slowly but steadily walk the road to reconstruction. However, a mysterious illness called Geostigma torments them. With no cure in sight, it brings death to the afflicted, one after another, robbing the people of their fledgling hope.","genre_ids":[16,28,12,14,878],"popularity":2.093,"vote_count":1211,"poster_path":"/pTIXM2yu8McSlcQVs1VjVSNC45x.jpg","release_date":"2005-07-14","vote_average":7.161,"backdrop_path":"/8xhgpYyNSX5sJi0P35hwL73QYOV.jpg","original_title":"Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children","original_language":"ja"},{"id":671,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","video":false,"overview":"Harry Potter has lived under the stairs at his aunt and uncle's house his whole life. But on his 11th birthday, he learns he's a powerful wizard—with a place waiting for him at the Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. As he learns to harness his newfound powers with the help of the school's kindly headmaster, Harry uncovers the truth about his parents' deaths—and about the villain who's to blame.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":22.7137,"vote_count":29166,"poster_path":"/wuMc08IPKEatf9rnMNXvIDxqP4W.jpg","release_date":"2001-11-16","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/1XAC6RPT01UX9EQGy2JVn5c8pgy.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","original_language":"en"},{"id":672,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets","video":false,"overview":"Cars fly, trees fight back, and a mysterious house-elf comes to warn Harry Potter at the start of his second year at Hogwarts. Adventure and danger await when bloody writing on a wall announces: The Chamber Of Secrets Has Been Opened. To save Hogwarts will require all of Harry, Ron and Hermione's magical abilities and courage.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":16.148,"vote_count":23265,"poster_path":"/sdEOH0992YZ0QSxgXNIGLq1ToUi.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-13","vote_average":7.704,"backdrop_path":"/1stUIsjawROZxjiCMtqqXqgfZWC.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets","original_language":"en"},{"id":673,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","video":false,"overview":"Year three at Hogwarts means new fun and challenges as Harry learns the delicate art of approaching a Hippogriff, transforming shape-shifting Boggarts into hilarity and even turning back time. But the term also brings danger: soul-sucking Dementors hover over the school, an ally of the accursed He-Who-Cannot-Be-Named lurks within the castle walls, and fearsome wizard Sirius Black escapes Azkaban. And Harry will confront them all.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":15.6854,"vote_count":22845,"poster_path":"/aWxwnYoe8p2d2fcxOqtvAtJ72Rw.jpg","release_date":"2004-05-31","vote_average":8.009,"backdrop_path":"/vbk5CfaAHOjQPSAcYm6AoRRz2Af.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","original_language":"en"},{"id":674,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","video":false,"overview":"When Harry Potter's name emerges from the Goblet of Fire, he becomes a competitor in a grueling battle for glory among three wizarding schools—the Triwizard Tournament. But since Harry never submitted his name for the Tournament, who did? Now Harry must confront a deadly dragon, fierce water demons and an enchanted maze only to find himself in the cruel grasp of He Who Must Not Be Named.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":17.271,"vote_count":21865,"poster_path":"/fECBtHlr0RB3foNHDiCBXeg9Bv9.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-16","vote_average":7.801,"backdrop_path":"/8f9dnOtpArDrOMEylpSN9Sc6fuz.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","original_language":"en"},{"id":675,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"Returning for his fifth year at Hogwarts, Harry is stunned to find that his warnings about the return of Lord Voldemort have been ignored. Left with no choice, Harry takes matters into his own hands, training a small group of motivated students to defend themselves against the Dark Arts.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":14.5713,"vote_count":20531,"poster_path":"/5aOyriWkPec0zUDxmHFP9qMmBaj.jpg","release_date":"2007-07-08","vote_average":7.672,"backdrop_path":"/pkxPkHOPJjOvzfQOclANEBT8OfK.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","original_language":"en"},{"id":765,"adult":false,"title":"Evil Dead II","video":false,"overview":"Ash Williams and his girlfriend Linda find a log cabin in the woods with a voice recording from an archeologist who had recorded himself reciting ancient chants from \"The Book of the Dead.\" As they play the recording an evil power is unleashed taking over Linda's body.","genre_ids":[27,35,14],"popularity":3.8434,"vote_count":3397,"poster_path":"/4zqCKJVHUolGs6C5AZwAZqLWixW.jpg","release_date":"1987-03-13","vote_average":7.545,"backdrop_path":"/dOvEJK2u0slAGTfhdZOjnNgCQet.jpg","original_title":"Evil Dead II","original_language":"en"},{"id":766,"adult":false,"title":"Army of Darkness","video":false,"overview":"Ash, a handsome, shotgun-toting, chainsaw-armed department store clerk, is time warped backwards into England's Dark Ages, where he romances a beauty and faces legions of the undead.","genre_ids":[14,27,35],"popularity":4.5693,"vote_count":3433,"poster_path":"/xsgTuAtR2zSH8Umg3jWZcZjlDpe.jpg","release_date":"1992-10-31","vote_average":7.261,"backdrop_path":"/5RPXs9g0sZ9Woo4pNLxdXdge7tc.jpg","original_title":"Army of Darkness","original_language":"en"},{"id":767,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","video":false,"overview":"As Lord Voldemort tightens his grip on both the Muggle and wizarding worlds, Hogwarts is no longer a safe haven. Harry suspects perils may even lie within the castle, but Dumbledore is more intent upon preparing him for the final battle fast approaching. Together they work to find the key to unlock Voldemorts defenses and to this end, Dumbledore recruits his old friend and colleague Horace Slughorn, whom he believes holds crucial information. Even as the decisive showdown looms, romance blossoms for Harry, Ron, Hermione and their classmates. Love is in the air, but danger lies ahead and Hogwarts may never be the same again.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":13.7456,"vote_count":20501,"poster_path":"/z7uo9zmQdQwU5ZJHFpv2Upl30i1.jpg","release_date":"2009-07-15","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/ze6Mx4QE5mQVXRYmG2flncqqle4.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","original_language":"en"},{"id":421594,"adult":false,"title":"Nana and Kaoru","video":false,"overview":"Kaoru is a 17-year-old boy with an SM fetish, secretly dreaming of an SM relationship with his childhood friend Nana. One day Kaoru's mother asks Nana to hide all his SM toys so that he will study for a change. However, Nana finds the leather one-piece that Kaoru bought and tries it on, but she accidentally locks it and does not have the key! This is the beginning of a very strange relationship...","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.7443,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/qCWi9MHrRctaCR82Rw3SZH20P2i.jpg","release_date":"2011-03-29","vote_average":4.8,"backdrop_path":"/u7rRtrJqngEFmptLsXQayC2cP4r.jpg","original_title":"ナナとカオル","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1961,"adult":false,"title":"My Name Is Bruce","video":false,"overview":"B Movie Legend Bruce Campbell is mistaken for his character Ash from the Evil Dead trilogy and forced to fight a real monster in a small town in Oregon.","genre_ids":[35,27,14],"popularity":0.8236,"vote_count":356,"poster_path":"/et2f1JBW533ZzYiCEA2T7nwzcs1.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-01","vote_average":5.795,"backdrop_path":"/snPM5sBGoZSm8g81yyqxsXmyzP6.jpg","original_title":"My Name Is Bruce","original_language":"en"},{"id":2006,"adult":false,"title":"Bell, Book and Candle","video":false,"overview":"Gillian Holroyd, a modern-day witch, becomes smitten with her handsome upstairs neighbor, Shep Henderson. Using her magical powers, she casts a love spell on him, only to face unexpected complications when genuine feelings emerge, threatening her supernatural abilities.","genre_ids":[35,14,10749],"popularity":0.897,"vote_count":239,"poster_path":"/z3MLtVFPT2wIkKCBSE2yBgDmeXI.jpg","release_date":"1958-12-25","vote_average":6.471,"backdrop_path":"/y5e5MTZtbMesmJ7EYgBdlceMcWq.jpg","original_title":"Bell, Book and Candle","original_language":"en"},{"id":2011,"adult":false,"title":"Persepolis","video":false,"overview":"In 1970s Iran, Marjane 'Marji' Satrapi watches events through her young eyes and her idealistic family of a long dream being fulfilled of the hated Shah's defeat in the Iranian Revolution of 1979. However as Marji grows up, she witnesses first hand how the new Iran, now ruled by Islamic fundamentalists, has become a repressive tyranny on its own.","genre_ids":[16,18],"popularity":1.6504,"vote_count":2098,"poster_path":"/aU8i2QAdTyRR1nYb36Gq51xXP8p.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-27","vote_average":7.887,"backdrop_path":"/6kqybERm5qi2jGpu8I7DaQPxpSU.jpg","original_title":"Persepolis","original_language":"fr"},{"id":766423,"adult":false,"title":"Puparia","video":false,"overview":"Something is about to change drastically, and the only thing to do is to witness it.","genre_ids":[16,18,14],"popularity":0.1282,"vote_count":59,"poster_path":"/3KRpbwNDrQ8cqKoVknoPqqtrpAO.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-23","vote_average":7.958,"backdrop_path":"/6HRvFDiP894qvRLMu0nM0WeNbiC.jpg","original_title":"Puparia","original_language":"ja"},{"id":949394,"adult":false,"title":"Ensemble Stars!! -Road to Show--","video":false,"overview":"Ensemble Square - a brand new building in the middle of the city where countless people come and go. It’s home to four offices belonging to idols who spend their days singing and dancing. Films starring the Ensemble Square idols have been nominated for the Idol Film Festival (IFF), an annual festival held in New York City, and representative idols are selected to attend. The boys jet off to NYC to attend the festival and reception party, and afterward, head out on the town to see the sights and sounds. But a suspicious shadow is creeping up on them…","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.7096,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/hW4Y4Fy8khf4D3tlvwV82txg1uy.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/eTfbiJANxSTnrISIL9JSGeI8uur.jpg","original_title":"あんさんぶるスターズ！！-Road to Show!!-","original_language":"ja"},{"id":919,"adult":false,"title":"Blood: The Last Vampire","video":false,"overview":"In Japan, the vampire-hunter Saya, who is a powerful original, is sent by her liaison with the government, David, posed as a teenage student to the Yokota High School on the eve of Halloween to hunt down vampires. Saya asks David to give a new katana to her. Soon she saves the school nurse Makiho Amano from two vampires disguised of classmates and Makiho witnesses her fight against the powerful demon.","genre_ids":[16,14,27],"popularity":1.1511,"vote_count":362,"poster_path":"/uRwR5lcl55n5JSaTiYPwp5KjP6A.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-18","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/17s9ojb8j8QnBGCfqDUJraXLlFi.jpg","original_title":"BLOOD THE LAST VAMPIRE","original_language":"ja"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0245429","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q155653","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/spirited-away","mydramalist_id":"16982","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/spirited_away"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":101334,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2003-07-17T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AT","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"